OL,3,CNHS staff in Cumbria walk out in pay
OL,4,Cdispute
OL,6,FNHS staff belonging to the GMB Union
OL,7,Fin Cumbria are on strike as part of an
OL,8,Fongoing dispute over pay banding.
OL,10,FOrthopaedic practitioners at North
OL,11,FCumbria Integrated Care Trust (NCIC)
OL,12,Fwalked out on Friday and will stay off
OL,13,Fwork until Monday as part of the
OL,14,Faction, with more strikes on the way
OL,15,Fif a resolution is not found.
OL,17,FThe GMB Union, which represents the
OL,18,Fstriking practitioners, claim they
OL,19,Flack proper job descriptions, which in
OL,20,Fturn affects their pay banding.
