OL,3,CNHS staff in Cumbria walk out in pay
OL,4,Cdispute
OL,6,FIn a statement, the Union said staff
OL,7,F"run complex clinics, like Virtual
OL,8,FFracture Clinics, yet are treated
OL,9,Funfairly, with management refusing to
OL,10,Fsign off their job description."
OL,12,FThis, they claim leads to unfair
OL,13,Flevels of pay for orthopaedic
OL,14,Fpractitioners working at NCIC as
OL,15,Fcompared to colleagues at other NHS
OL,16,Ftrusts.
