OL,3,CNHS staff in Cumbria walk out in pay
OL,4,Cdispute
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News Border, branch
OL,7,Fsecretary Claire Robbins said: "The
OL,8,Forthopaedic practitioners lack a job
OL,9,Fdescription that reflects their role
OL,10,Fin fair pay."
OL,12,FShe added that strike action would
OL,13,Fcontinue for "as long as it needs to."
OL,15,F"This particular first round, is
OL,16,Fencompassed Friday, Saturday, Sunday
OL,17,Fand Monday, but as as long as it needs
OL,18,Fto, until we can reach resolution,
OL,19,Fwhich we are really keen to do."
