OL,3,CNHS staff in Cumbria walk out in pay
OL,4,Cdispute
OL,6,FIn a statement NCIC said it was aiming
OL,7,Fto reach a "fair" resolution with
OL,8,Fstaff.
OL,10,FThey said: "We acknowledge the lack of
OL,11,Fa nationally recognised job profile
OL,12,Ffor orthopaedic practitioners and the
OL,13,Fvariations in banding across different
OL,14,FTrusts.
OL,16,F"We have previously reviewed the job
OL,17,Fdescriptions and banding to make sure
OL,18,Fthey are consistent with national
OL,19,Fpractices and reflect the
OL,20,Fresponsibilities undertaken by
OL,21,Fcolleagues.
